cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR 

This paper is about neural architecture search for text representation, which is a topic related to natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of automatic search algorithms and the importance of the search space, which are topics related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, respectively. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on various public datasets, which is a topic related to information retrieval. Therefore, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category.
